### DB

<br>

### bdetail

<br>

```sql
create or replace view bdetail as
select bid,btype,cname,btitle,bcontent,bwriter,t_name,view_ct,create_date,modify_date,b.st
from board b
join test on(t_no=bwriter)
join category using(cid)
where b.st = 'Y';
commit;
``
